<sect2>
<title>Installation de xpdf</title>

<para>Installez xpdf en lançant les commandes suivantes:</para>

<para><screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc --mandir=/usr/share/man  \
    --with-freetype2-includes=/usr/include/freetype2 \
    --with-freetype2-library=/usr/lib \
    --with-appdef-dir=/usr/X11R6/lib/X11/app-defaults/ &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</userinput></screen></para>

</sect2>
